to check the status of a local repository, use the comand git status

to add invidual files or globablly, use the comand git add

to add comments to te commit, use the comand git commit --amend 

to upload changes to a remote repository, use the comand push git

to create branch use the command git branch <branch-name>
to browse branches use the comand git branch -a 
to delete branch use command   git branch -d <branch_name_to_delete>

to roll back a repository to a specific commit use the comand git reset --hard <old-commit-id> 


